{"tid":2418280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★2020年7至11月期間 因移民及離港升學而退學，較2019年同期大增50%","createTime":"2021-02-22T13:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T06:51:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb5fbb9acdebd78305c7ca1e8cbe81628bcaaa4","tid":2418280,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"調查發現，於2020年7至11月期間，各中學共有1,474名學生退學，較2019年同期的1,195名學生退學增加23%。而報告進一步分析學生退學的原因指出，去年7至11月共有723名學生因為離港，包括<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>移民及到海外升學而退學，較2019年同期的475人大增5成</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦統計了教師除退休外的離職情況，在2020年7至11月，各中學共有235名教師離職，較2019年同期的205人增加15%。結果顯示，逾80%中學校長預期學生退學數字在未來會持續上升，亦有逾70%中學校長估計教師離職數字會繼續增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210222/bkn-20210222175527275-0222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210222%2Fbkn-20210222175527275-0222_00822_001.html&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=510dea8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210222/bkn-20210222175527275-0222_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0803d3483ec3c2684ac3c9e87b47b36193c1c138","tid":2418280,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca74e50bfe2d1ee3f01e45dd334154ad6d270af8","tid":2418280,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl